1165
01:29:40,130 --> 01:29:41,460
開火吧
{\fntahoma\fs16\bord0\1c&H00FFFF&\b0}Fire at will!{\r}

1166
01:30:21,880 --> 01:30:23,300
飛蟲來襲
{\fntahoma\fs16\bord0\1c&H00FFFF&\b0}Incoming!{\r}

1167
01:30:55,340 --> 01:30:57,540
瑞哥 連線好了嗎? 
