{\fntahoma\fs16\bord0\1c&H00FFFF&\b0}Hold here! Hold what you've got!{\r}

1181
01:32:43,360 --> 01:32:44,690
彈藥快沒了
{\fntahoma\fs16\bord0\1c&H00FFFF&\b0}Running low!{\r}

