{\fntahoma\fs16\bord0\1c&H00FFFF&\b0}Move, move, move!{\r}

1186
01:33:31,410 --> 01:33:33,900
快登機 撤
{\fntahoma\fs16\bord0\1c&H00FFFF&\b0}Fall back to the boat! Haul ass!{\r}

1187
01:33:47,630 --> 01:33:49,670
- 我的天 - 哦
{\fntahoma\fs16\bord0\1c&H00FFFF&\b0}- Oh, my God! - Oh!{\r}

1188
01:33:53,350 --> 01:33:55,920
- 把他拉上來 - 快
{\fntahoma\fs16\bord0\1c&H00FFFF&\b0}- Get him outta there! Pull! - Come on!{\r}

1189
01:34:02,110 --> 01:34:04,230
瑞哥 瑞哥
