{\fntahoma\fs16\bord0\1c&H00FFFF&\b0}- Yeah! - Dizzy!{\r}

1193
01:35:04,920 --> 01:35:06,660
不!
{\fntahoma\fs16\bord0\1c&H00FFFF&\b0}No!{\r}

1194
01:35:06,750 --> 01:35:09,540
王牌 幫我拉住她
{\fntahoma\fs16\bord0\1c&H00FFFF&\b0}Ace, help me! Hold her down!{\r}

1195
01:35:14,510 --> 01:35:16,670
把她抬上機
{\fntahoma\fs16\bord0\1c&H00FFFF&\b0}Move! Get her into the boat!{\r}

1196
01:35:18,260 --> 01:35:20,060
蒂絲 千萬別死
{\fntahoma\fs16\bord0\1c&H00FFFF&\b0}Come on, Diz! Don't die on me!{\r}

1197
01:35:20,140 --> 01:35:21,420
把她抬走 快
{\fntahoma\fs16\bord0\1c&H00FFFF&\b0}Let's get her out! Let's go, let's go!{\r}

1198
01:35:27,860 --> 01:35:29,570
快上去
{\fntahoma\fs16\bord0\1c&H00FFFF&\b0}Let's go! Get aboard!{\r}

1199
01:35:31,190 --> 01:35:33,070
你們 快點...
{\fntahoma\fs16\bord0\1c&H00FFFF&\b0}Tower, let's go!{\r}

1200
01:35:39,200 --> 01:35:43,120
快來吧
{\fntahoma\fs16\bord0\1c&H00FFFF&\b0}Let's move it, tower! Run!{\r}

1201
01:35:49,170 --> 01:35:50,550
升空
