{\fntahoma\fs16\bord0\1c&H00FFFF&\b0}Rodger Young, we have an official request...{\r}

1215
01:37:38,860 --> 01:37:41,980
機動部隊要求轟炸P星球
{\fntahoma\fs16\bord0\1c&H00FFFF&\b0}by the Mobile Infantry to commence bombardment of Planet P.{\r}

1216
01:37:43,330 --> 01:37:45,730
我以為你死了
{\fntahoma\fs16\bord0\1c&H00FFFF&\b0}I thought you were dead.{\r}

1217
01:37:45,830 --> 01:37:48,910
我沒死 很多戰友都死了
{\fntahoma\fs16\bord0\1c&H00FFFF&\b0}I'm not, but a lot of my troopers are.{\r}

1218
01:37:49,000 --> 01:37:50,960
不行
{\fntahoma\fs16\bord0\1c&H00FFFF&\b0}Negative on your request, DeRuyter.{\r}

1219
01:37:51,040 --> 01:37:53,250
元帥另有安排
{\fntahoma\fs16\bord0\1c&H00FFFF&\b0}The Sky Marshal has other plans for Planet P.{\r}

1220
01:37:53,340 --> 01:37:54,580
歡迎回來
{\fntahoma\fs16\bord0\1c&H00FFFF&\b0}Welcome back.{\r}

1221
01:37:54,670 --> 01:37:57,760
機動部隊負責死 艦隊負責飛
{\fntahoma\fs16\bord0\1c&H00FFFF&\b0}MI does the dying. Fleet just does the flying.{\r}

1222
01:37:57,840 --> 01:37:59,750
等等 有動靜了
{\fntahoma\fs16\bord0\1c&H00FFFF&\b0}Hold on. Something's up.{\r}

1223
01:37:59,840 --> 01:38:02,330
