01:39:31,040 --> 01:39:33,830
放下
{\fntahoma\fs16\bord0\1c&H00FFFF&\b0}Order arms!{\r}

1237
01:39:37,210 --> 01:39:38,960
向左轉
{\fntahoma\fs16\bord0\1c&H00FFFF&\b0}Left face!{\r}

1238
01:39:53,060 --> 01:39:55,140
- 立正 - 繼續
{\fntahoma\fs16\bord0\1c&H00FFFF&\b0}- Officer on deck! - Carry on.{\r}

1239
