{\fntahoma\fs16\bord0\1c&H00FFFF&\b0}Burial detail dismissed.{\r}

1240
01:40:06,410 --> 01:40:08,650
稍息
{\fntahoma\fs16\bord0\1c&H00FFFF&\b0}At ease.{\r}

1241
01:40:08,740 --> 01:40:11,990
