1248
01:40:28,140 --> 01:40:31,510
我們找不到首腦就不能進行攻擊
{\fntahoma\fs16\bord0\1c&H00FFFF&\b0}We couldn't afford to launch an operation if there wasn't one.{\r}

1249
01:40:33,430 --> 01:40:36,850
你不茍同 很遺憾
{\fntahoma\fs16\bord0\1c&H00FFFF&\b0}You don't approve. Well, too bad.{\r}

1250
01:40:36,940 --> 01:40:38,850
事關人類存亡
{\fntahoma\fs16\bord0\1c&H00FFFF&\b0}We're in this for the species, boys and girls.{\r}

1251
01:40:38,940 --> 01:40:41,310
它們數量眾多
{\fntahoma\fs16\bord0\1c&H00FFFF&\b0}It's simple numbers. They have more.{\r}

1252
01:40:41,400 --> 01:40:43,140
我每天都得決定...
{\fntahoma\fs16\bord0\1c&H00FFFF&\b0}And every day I have to make decisions...{\r}

1253
01:40:43,240 --> 01:40:46,070
派你這種人去送死
