1263
01:41:17,770 --> 01:41:19,560
你要小心 強尼
{\fntahoma\fs16\bord0\1c&H00FFFF&\b0}Take care of yourself,Johnny.{\r}

1264
01:41:19,650 --> 01:41:21,440
後會有期
{\fntahoma\fs16\bord0\1c&H00FFFF&\b0}I'll see you again.{\r}

1265
01:41:34,620 --> 01:41:36,280
立正
{\fntahoma\fs16\bord0\1c&H00FFFF&\b0}Officer on deck!{\r}

1266
01:41:53,720 --> 01:41:57,310
